ays - had anything to spare - but we used to live - it was a bit harder living but the food then - had some goodness in it. See, the children nowaday}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12060953\charrsid3099254 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 , I shouldn't ought to say this though, there are a lot of children nowaday}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12060953\charrsid3099254 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 
 are - are - reared up on chocolate - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12060953\charrsid3099254 \'e9clairs}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254  and sponge cake.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
