\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12409093 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 
Oh well, a set meal and you - well - you had to eat your set meal, mother never made any - any meal for one more than the other, I mean to say that you - there was a meal and - served for all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 What would your parents say if you left some food uneaten on the plate?
