Oh - well - we had table - etiquette they call it or something isn't it, yes, we had that, yes, we had to - though we was a big family, and mother and father and back in earlier days, they would see that - we went to 
the table and behaved ourselves to the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Were you ever allowed to bring toys or books to the table?
