\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12409093 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Well I weren't old enough for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 It was just a social club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12409093 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Yes, yes, yes, yes, yes, yes, yes, yes. Yes, you mean total abst}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12060953\charrsid3099254 ine}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 nce. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 At home was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12409093 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Well I'm afraid - I'm afraid not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12409093 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Well Our Father which art in Heaven, or Gentle Jesus when we was younger, meek and mild.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Did you ever have family prayers?
