l I can mind a few arguments, I don't - wouldn't say that there was anybody - I mean beaten up through it but I can mind 'em a little bit rough like in talking and all like and - bit shoving, bit - I mean scuffle what you call but nothing - serious. Not l
i
ke down Camborne here years ago - I - I - I mean students down there and the Camborne used to - the Camborne chaps used to drive them down there and - smash the windows in the students and they had a good old go back in they days before the first war. Cha
ps from Camborne and the students. And I - I've never seen it but I have heard - that the - that the Bobbies down there have had their helmets - knocked off in the fountain and all, I've heard they things but - I've never seen it myself, no, I've never -

