\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 You were saying about your grandmother's funeral, some people used to take children to see
 the corpse in the old days, would that have happened to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12409093 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 
Oh well, not a child, a young child, but the - but the neighbours or anyone of the family would come in just before the corpse like was - had to be taken out the house like, and the - and 
the undertaker was there, and - take the cover up and so any - anybody could have a look like and - well - by that time it was ready for to put the put the cover down again and - and screw it up ready for the - funeral. That all right?
