Oh with the boys in Troon like - ah well Mr Berryman now, he lived down Dolcoath Avenue, he's the same age as me, George what they used to call, and he used to sing in the choir when I did }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14381211\charrsid3099254 
\endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254  alto}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14381211\charrsid3099254  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 up - up united Methodist choir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 That would be neighbours?
