\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters?
