\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12409093 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Well - no, we was a lot of boys like and we 
used to - oh well, chat to each other like if there was a little bit of argument - might have been on - on both sides but that was always - nothing in they days, we used to get on - on the whole - very well together.
