\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14381211\charrsid3099254 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 wery Field, behind Fore Street houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 That's where they played cricket?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12409093 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Yes.
