nd was muddy well - you're bound to get - a bit dirty, but - but no dirtier than we - should ought to be like. Oh yes, used to play marbles. Men who do playing marbles, the likes of Mr Rowe, Mr Edward Johns and - and - well about half a dozen men and used
 
to have a great - circle, a - a ring what they call, with some marbles in the middle and you had to fire at the - into the ring, to them marbles, why try to knock them out the ring. And if you did 'course the - the marbles is yours if you could knock them
 out the ring.
