{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Chapel Square{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, Troon here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423890 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254 Were you free to play with anyone you pleased?
