\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10693638\charrsid3099254  in there and - and men in there selling - china, tick-tacks what they call and - all these things in them days, what - leaving out the ordinary stalls that you hav
e in the ordinary tea treats. And then - chip vans in there and - and never needn't go into the restaurants and have a good meal if you was in a hurry, you could have a - well go to a chip van and have a bag of chips and and on your way, and - well, there
 
